<section class="warranty-body">
  <div class="container-narrow">

    <div class="warranty-intro reveal">
      <span class="section-label">Our Commitment</span>
      <h2>Built to Last. Backed to Prove It.</h2>
      <p>MUNLER offers a 5-year warranty on all products against defects in materials and workmanship. We specify 304-grade stainless steel and ecological silver glass precisely because they are built to last — and our warranty is an extension of that conviction.</p>
      <p>If a defect covered under this warranty arises within five years of your purchase date, we will repair or replace the item at no cost to you.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="warranty-grid reveal">
      <div class="warranty-card warranty-card--covered">
        <div class="warranty-card-header">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
          <h3>What's Covered</h3>
        </div>
        <ul>
          <li>Manufacturing defects in materials or workmanship</li>
          <li>Frame structural failure under normal use</li>
          <li>Corrosion of stainless steel frames under normal indoor or sheltered outdoor conditions</li>
          <li>Discolouration of mirror surface due to production fault</li>
          <li>Hardware failures (fixings, wall mounts, brackets) supplied with the product</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="warranty-card warranty-card--excluded">
        <div class="warranty-card-header">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg>
          <h3>What's Not Covered</h3>
        </div>
        <ul>
          <li>Accidental damage, breakage, or misuse</li>
          <li>Normal wear, scratches, or surface marks from everyday use</li>
          <li>Damage caused by improper installation</li>
          <li>Exposure to harsh chemicals or abrasive cleaning products</li>
          <li>Damage resulting from modifications to the product</li>
          <li>Products purchased from unauthorised resellers</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="warranty-claim reveal">
      <span class="section-label">Making a Claim</span>
      <h2>How to Claim</h2>
      <div class="warranty-steps">
        <div class="warranty-step">
          <span class="warranty-step-num">01</span>
          <div class="warranty-step-body">
            <h4>Contact Us</h4>
            <p>Email <a href="mailto:info@munler.co.uk">info@munler.co.uk</a> with your order number, a description of the issue, and photographs of the defect.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="warranty-step">
          <span class="warranty-step-num">02</span>
          <div class="warranty-step-body">
            <h4>Assessment</h4>
            <p>Our team will review your claim within 3–5 working days and confirm whether it falls within the warranty terms.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="warranty-step">
          <span class="warranty-step-num">03</span>
          <div class="warranty-step-body">
            <h4>Resolution</h4>
            <p>Where a valid claim is confirmed, we will arrange a repair, replacement, or — where neither is possible — a full refund of the original purchase price.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="warranty-note reveal">
      <p>This warranty is in addition to your statutory rights under UK consumer law and does not affect them. The warranty applies to the original purchaser only and is non-transferable. Proof of purchase is required for all claims.</p>
      <p>For questions about your warranty, contact us at <a href="mailto:info@munler.co.uk">info@munler.co.uk</a> or visit our <a href="/pages/contact">contact page</a>.</p>
    </div>

